87
00:10:20,850 --> 00:10:23,330
Ona---Ona---

88
00:10:35,570 --> 00:10:38,100
Je v poriadku, či nie?

89
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:39,790
Našťastie, je v poriadku.

90
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:43,620
Ty? Vy sa poznáte?

91
00:10:43,620 --> 00:10:45,320
Ak odhadujem správne,

92
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:49,040
mala by to byť princezná Cnostná z Megrezu, ktorá sa schovávala v paláci Hlbokej vody,

93
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:52,310
