124
00:14:18,790 --> 00:14:21,720
Je tam duch! V Hale presvietenej lúčmi je duch!

125
00:14:22,820 --> 00:14:25,100
Je tam duch! Je tam duch!

126
00:14:25,100 --> 00:14:27,060
Je tam duch!

127
